x844.jpg 940w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/japanese-inspired-house-koi-pond-black-framed-windows-240524-510-10-800x718.jpg 800w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/japanese-inspired-house-koi-pond-black-framed-windows-240524-510-10-768x690.jpg 768w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/japanese-inspired-house-koi-pond-black-framed-windows-240524-510-10-1536x1379.jpg 1536w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\"/\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cp\u003eThe living room sits at the edge of the garden, opening wide to the outdoors through retractable doors that erase the line between interior and landscape. With minimal barriers, the family is encouraged to live with the seasons, enjoying soft breezes and the filtered light of the garden. The room’s simple palette of timber, charcoal and white allows the greenery beyond to become the main focus, reinforcing the home’s connection to nature.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1920\" height=\"1763\" src=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/japanese-inspired-house-living-room-240524-510-11.jpg\" alt=\"A bold yet tranquil living room blends Japanese minimalism with graphic modernism, exposed beams, a sculptural striped table, and black-framed windows offer strong contrasts softened by warm timber floors and a calming courtyard view.\" srcset=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/japanese-inspired-house-living-room-240524-510-11.jpg 1920w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/japanese-inspired-house-living-room-240524-510-11-940x863.jpg 940w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/japanese-inspired-house-living-room-240524-510-11-800x735.jpg 800w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/japanese-inspired-house-living-room-240524-510-11-768x705.jpg 768w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/japanese-inspired-house-living-room-240524-510-11-1536x1410.jpg 1536w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\"/\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1703\" height=\"2560\" src=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/japanese-inspired-house-living-room-240524-510-12.jpg\" alt=\"A bold yet tranquil living room blends Japanese minimalism with graphic modernism, exposed beams, a sculptural striped table, and black-framed windows offer strong contrasts softened by warm timber floors and a calming courtyard view.\" srcset=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/japanese-inspired-house-living-room-240524-510-12.jpg 1703w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/japanese-inspired-house-living-room-240524-510-12-940x1413.jpg 940w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/japanese-inspired-house-living-room-240524-510-12-800x1203.jpg 800w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/japanese-inspired-house-living-room-240524-510-12-768x1154.jpg 768w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/japanese-inspired-house-living-room-240524-510-12-1022x1536.jpg 1022w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/japanese-inspired-house-living-room-240524-510-12-1362x2048.jpg 1362w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1703px) 100vw, 1703px\"/\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cp\u003eOne of the most versatile spaces in the addition is the Tatami room. Framed by traditional shoji screen doors, the room can be fully closed for privacy or opened to merge with adjacent spaces. It serves as a guest room, retreat or extension of the living area, offering adaptability without visual clutter. The sliding screens filter light, casting delicate patterns throughout the day while maintaining a sense of calm enclosure.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1920\" height=\"1949\" src=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/japanese-inspired-house-living-room-shoji-screen-tatami-240524-510-13.jpg\" alt=\"A serene fusion of traditional and modern, tatami flooring and shoji screens frame a sunlit room.\" srcset=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/japanese-inspired-house-living-room-shoji-screen-tatami-240524-510-13.jpg 1920w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/japanese-inspired-house-living-room-shoji-screen-tatami-240524-510-13-940x954.jpg 940w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/japanese-inspired-house-living-room-shoji-screen-tatami-240524-510-13-800x812.jpg 800w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/japanese-inspired-house-living-room-shoji-screen-tatami-240524-510-13-768x780.jpg 768w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/japanese-inspired-house-living-room-shoji-screen-tatami-240524-510-13-1513x1536.jpg 1513w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\"/\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1920\" height=\"1700\" src=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/japanese-inspired-house-living-room-shoji-screen-tatami-240524-510-14.jpg\" alt=\"A serene fusion of traditional and modern, tatami flooring and shoji screens frame a sunlit room.\" srcset=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/japanese-inspired-house-living-room-shoji-screen-tatami-240524-510-14.jpg 1920w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/japanese-inspired-house-living-room-shoji-screen-tatami-240524-510-14-940x832.jpg 940w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/japanese-inspired-house-living-room-shoji-screen-tatami-240524-510-14-800x708.jpg 800w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/japanese-inspired-house-living-room-shoji-screen-tatami-240524-510-14-768x680.jpg 768w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/japanese-inspired-house-living-room-shoji-screen-tatami-240524-510-14-1536x1360.jpg 1536w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\"/\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cp\u003ePositioned at the core of the new addition, the kitchen balances clean-lined functionality with a warm material palette. Timber joinery and stone surfaces reflect the home’s natural sensibilities, while thoughtful storage and layout support family life. Framed views toward the pond and garden reinforce a feeling of quiet connection even in the most active part of the house.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1920\" height=\"1278\" src=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/japanese-inspired-kitchen-koi-pond-240524-510-15.jpg\" alt=\"This Japanese-inspired kitchen has views of a tranquil reflection pond, blending natural textures with clean, modern lines. Black-framed windows flood the space with light, while the butcher-block island adds warmth and artisanal character.\" srcset=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/japanese-inspired-kitchen-koi-pond-240524-510-15.jpg 1920w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/japanese-inspired-kitchen-koi-pond-240524-510-15-940x626.jpg 940w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/japanese-inspired-kitchen-koi-pond-240524-510-15-800x533.jpg 800w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/japanese-inspired-kitchen-koi-pond-240524-510-15-768x511.jpg 768w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/japanese-inspired-kitchen-koi-pond-240524-510-15-1536x1022.jpg 1536w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\"/\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1920\" height=\"1310\" src=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/japanese-inspired-kitchen-koi-pond-240524-510-16.jpg\" alt=\"This Japanese-inspired kitchen has views of a tranquil reflection pond, blending natural textures with clean, modern lines. Black-framed windows flood the space with light, while the butcher-block island adds warmth and artisanal character.\" srcset=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/japanese-inspired-kitchen-koi-pond-240524-510-16.jpg 1920w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/japanese-inspired-kitchen-koi-pond-240524-510-16-940x641.jpg 940w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/japanese-inspired-kitchen-koi-pond-240524-510-16-800x546.jpg 800w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/japanese-inspired-kitchen-koi-pond-240524-510-16-768x524.jpg 768w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/japanese-inspired-kitchen-koi-pond-240524-510-16-1536x1048.jpg 1536w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\"/\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1696\" height=\"2560\" src=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/japanese-inspired-kitchen-240524-510-17.jpg\" alt=\"This Japanese-inspired kitchen has views of a tranquil reflection pond, blending natural textures with clean, modern lines. Black-framed windows flood the space with light, while the butcher-block island adds warmth and artisanal character.\" srcset=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/japanese-inspired-kitchen-240524-510-17.jpg 1696w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/japanese-inspired-kitchen-240524-510-17-940x1419.jpg 940w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/japanese-inspired-kitchen-240524-510-17-800x1208.jpg 800w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/japanese-inspired-kitchen-240524-510-17-768x1159.jpg 768w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/japanese-inspired-kitchen-240524-510-17-1018x1536.jpg 1018w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/japanese-inspired-kitchen-240524-510-17-1357x2048.jpg 1357w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1696px) 100vw, 1696px\"/\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cp\u003eThe dining area is calm and restrained, defined by clean lines, soft light and a refined palette. A round table sits beneath a woven pendant, flanked by sculptural chairs in mismatched finishes that add quiet character without disrupting harmony. Large framed windows bring in diffused daylight while offering glimpses of the garden beyond.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1920\" height=\"1249\" src=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/japanese-inspired-dining-room-240524-510-18.jpg\" alt=\"The dining area is calm and restrained, defined by clean lines, soft light and a refined palette. A round table sits beneath a woven pendant, flanked by sculptural chairs in mismatched finishes that add quiet character without disrupting harmony.\" srcset=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/japanese-inspired-dining-room-240524-510-18.jpg 1920w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/japanese-inspired-dining-room-240524-510-18-940x611.jpg 940w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/japanese-inspired-dining-room-240524-510-18-800x520.jpg 800w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/japanese-inspired-dining-room-240524-510-18-768x500.jpg 768w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/japanese-inspired-dining-room-240524-510-18-1536x999.jpg 1536w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\"/\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cp\u003eA dedicated office space offers a quiet retreat for focused work. While compact, the room is designed for calm productivity, continuing the broader themes of minimalism and visual clarity.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1718\" height=\"2560\" src=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/japanese-inspired-home-office-240524-510-19.jpg\" alt=\"A dedicated office space offers a quiet retreat for focused work. While compact, the room is designed for calm productivity, continuing the broader themes of minimalism and visual clarity.\" srcset=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/japanese-inspired-home-office-240524-510-19.jpg 1718w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/japanese-inspired-home-office-240524-510-19-940x1401.jpg 940w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/japanese-inspired-home-office-240524-510-19-800x1192.jpg 800w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/japanese-inspired-home-office-240524-510-19-768x1144.jpg 768w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/japanese-inspired-home-office-240524-510-19-1031x1536.jpg 1031w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/japanese-inspired-home-office-240524-510-19-1374x2048.jpg 1374w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1718px) 100vw, 1718px\"/\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cp\u003eMovement through the new wing is guided by a simple hallway that offers layered views across the koi pond and into other parts of the home.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1741\" height=\"2560\" src=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/japanese-inspired-interior-240524-510-20.jpg\" alt=\"Movement through the new wing is guided by a simple hallway with wood floors and white walls.\" srcset=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/japanese-inspired-interior-240524-510-20.jpg 1741w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/japanese-inspired-interior-240524-510-20-940x1382.jpg 940w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/japanese-inspired-interior-240524-510-20-800x1176.jpg 800w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/japanese-inspired-interior-240524-510-20-768x1129.jpg 768w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/japanese-inspired-interior-240524-510-20-1045x1536.jpg 1045w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/japanese-inspired-interior-240524-510-20-1393x2048.jpg 1393w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1741px) 100vw, 1741px\"/\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cp\u003eThis bathroom pairs calm materials with precise detailing. Soft light filters through frosted glass, illuminating the stone and white finishes. A single ikebana arrangement adds a quiet, sculptural gesture that echoes the home’s connection to nature and simplicity.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1900\" height=\"2560\" src=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/japanese-inspired-bathroom-240524-510-21.jpg\" alt=\"This bathroom pairs calm materials with precise detailing. Soft light filters through frosted glass, illuminating the stone and white finishes. A single ikebana arrangement adds a quiet, sculptural gesture that echoes the home’s connection to nature and simplicity.\" srcset=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/japanese-inspired-bathroom-240524-510-21.jpg 1900w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/japanese-inspired-bathroom-240524-510-21-940x1267.jpg 940w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/japanese-inspired-bathroom-240524-510-21-800x1078.jpg 800w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/japanese-inspired-bathroom-240524-510-21-768x1035.jpg 768w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/japanese-inspired-bathroom-240524-510-21-1140x1536.jpg 1140w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/japanese-inspired-bathroom-240524-510-21-1520x2048.jpg 1520w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1900px) 100vw, 1900px\"/\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cp\u003eThe floor plan unfolds as a seamless sequence of connected rooms, where sliding elements and consistent materials create an intuitive sense of openness, flexibility and flow within a compact footprint.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1920\" height=\"1068\" src=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/japanese-inspired-house-extension-floor-plan-240524-510-22.jpg\" alt=\"The floor plan unfolds as a seamless sequence of connected rooms, where sliding elements and consistent materials create an intuitive sense of openness, flexibility and flow within a compact footprint.\" srcset=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/japanese-inspired-house-extension-floor-plan-240524-510-22.jpg 1920w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/japanese-inspired-house-extension-floor-plan-240524-510-22-940x523.jpg 940w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/japanese-inspired-house-extension-floor-plan-240524-510-22-800x445.jpg 800w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/japanese-inspired-house-extension-floor-plan-240524-510-22-768x427.jpg 768w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/japanese-inspired-house-extension-floor-plan-240524-510-22-1536x854.jpg 1536w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\"/\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cp\u003eJapan House is a study in architectural restraint, cultural depth and spatial grace. Rooted in passive design principles and shaped by a deep appreciation for Japanese traditions, the project delivers far more than extra space, it offers a new way of living.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003chr/\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003ch6\u003ePhotography by \u003ca href=\"https://katherinelu.com\"\u003eKatherine Lu\u003c/a\u003e | Architect: \u003ca href=\"http://sandboxstudio.com.au\"\u003eSandbox Studio\u003c/a\u003e | Stylist: \u003ca href=\"http://meganmorton.com\"\u003eMegan Morton STYLIST\u003c/a\u003e | Builder: \u003ca href=\"https://www.instagram.com/jcg_australia/\"\u003eJCG Australia\u003c/a\u003e | Engineer: \u003ca href=\"https://www.bmybuildingconsultants.com.au\"\u003eBMY Building Consultants\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/h6\u003e\n\t\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e",
